# Styling & Design System Rules for CaloriTrack

## Color Palette Usage
- **Primary:** #7C3AED (Purple-600) - Main actions, accents
- **Primary Dark:** #6D28D9 (Purple-700) - Pressed states
- **Primary Light:** #A78BFA (Purple-400) - Hover states
- **Gradient:** #7C3AED to #EC4899 - Special highlights
- **Background:** #FFFFFF - Main app background
- **Surface:** #FEFEFE - Cards, elevated surfaces
- **Text Primary:** #1E293B - Main text, headings
- **Text Secondary:** #64748B - Supporting text
- **Border:** #E2E8F0 - Input borders, dividers

## Typography Scale
- **Font Family:** Inter (system fallback: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto)
- **Font Sizes:**
  - xs: 12px - Tiny labels, captions
  - sm: 14px - Small text, descriptions
  - base: 16px - Body text, default size
  - lg: 18px - Subheadings, emphasis
  - xl: 20px - Section headings
  - 2xl: 24px - Page titles
  - 3xl: 30px - Hero titles
- **Font Weights:**
  - Regular: 400
  - Medium: 500 - UI elements, buttons
  - Semibold: 600 - Headings, important labels
  - Bold: 700 - Strong emphasis
- **Line Heights:**
  - Tight: 1.25 - Large headings
  - Normal: 1.5 - Body text
  - Relaxed: 1.75 - Descriptive text

## Spacing System
- **Base:** 4px unit scale
- **Scale:** 1 (4px), 2 (8px), 3 (12px), 4 (16px), 5 (20px), 6 (24px), 8 (32px), 10 (40px), 12 (48px), 16 (64px), 20 (80px)
- **Usage:**
  - Component padding: 16px (4)
  - Section spacing: 32px (8)
  - Page margins: 24px (6)

## Border Radius
- **sm:** 4px - Small elements, tags
- **md:** 8px - Buttons, input fields
- **lg:** 12px - Cards, larger elements
- **xl:** 16px - Modals, special containers
- **full:** 9999px - Pills, avatars

## Shadow System
- **sm:** 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) - Subtle lift
- **md:** 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06) - Cards
- **lg:** 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) - Modals
- **xl:** 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) - Overlays

